{
  "chapter": "078",
  "title": "春申君列传",
  "translations": {
    "1": {
      "title": "春申君使秦",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">春申君</span>是<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>人，名<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：黄歇\">歇（黄歇）</span>，姓<span class=\"dynasty\" title=\"氏族\">黄氏</span>。游学博闻，事奉<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">楚顷襄王</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">顷襄王</span>认为<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：黄歇\">歇（黄歇）</span>有辩才，派他出使<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">秦昭王</span>派<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">白起</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">韩</span>、<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">魏</span>，在<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">华阳</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">败</span>之，<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">禽</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">魏</span>将<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">芒卯</span>，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">韩</span>、<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">魏</span>归服事奉<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">秦昭王</span>正命<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">白起</span>与<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">韩</span>、<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">魏</span>共同<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">伐</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>，未出发，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>使<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">黄歇</span>恰到<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>，听到了<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>的计划。这时，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>已经先派<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">白起</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>，<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">取</span><span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">巫</span>、<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">黔中</span>之郡，<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">拔</span><span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">鄢</span><span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">郢</span>，东至<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">竟陵</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">楚顷襄王</span>东迁至<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">陈</span>县治事。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">黄歇</span>见<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">楚怀王</span>被<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>诱骗入朝，竟被欺骗，最后死于<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">顷襄王</span>是他的<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">子</span>，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>轻视他，怕<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>一举兵就<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">灭</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：黄歇\">歇（黄歇）</span>于是上书游说<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">秦昭王</span>说："
    },
    "2": {
      "title": "两虎相斗",
      "text": "<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">天下</span>没有比<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>、<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>更强的了。如今听说大王要<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">伐</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>，这就像两虎相斗。两虎相斗而劣狗受益，不如善待<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>。<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">臣</span>请说其理由：<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">臣</span>听说事物到极点就会反向，冬夏便是；积累到极限就危险，堆积玉器便是。如今大国之地，占<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">天下</span>两边，自有生<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">民</span>以来，<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">万乘</span>之国还未曾有过。<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">先帝</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">文王</span>、<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">庄王</span>之身，<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">三世（时长）</span>不轻易把土地和<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>相接，以切断合纵之关键。<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">今王</span>派<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">盛桥</span>到<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">韩</span>任事，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">盛桥</span>以其地归<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>，这是王不用<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">甲</span>兵，不显威势，就得到<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">百里</span>之地。王可算是有能力。王又举<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">甲</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">魏</span>，堵塞<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">大梁</span>之门，攻取<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">河内</span>，<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">拔</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">燕</span>、<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">酸枣</span>、<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">虚</span>、<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">桃</span>，入<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">邢</span>，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">魏</span>之兵纷纷飞逃而不敢相救。王的功绩可算多了。王休<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">甲</span>息兵，<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">二年（时长）</span>而后再动；又并吞<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">蒲</span>、<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">衍</span>、<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">首</span>、<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">垣</span>，以兵临<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">仁</span>、<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">平丘</span>，<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">黄</span>、<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">济阳</span>固守而<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">魏</span>氏归服；王又割<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">濮</span>"
    },
    "3": {
      "title": "威震天下",
      "text": "之北，贯注齐<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>之要道，切断<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>赵之脊梁，<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">天下</span>五合六聚而不敢来救。王的威势也达到极致了。"
    },
    "4": {
      "title": "恐其有后患",
      "text": "王若能持功守威，裁抑<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">取</span>之心而增益<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">仁义</span>之地，使国家没有后患，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">三王</span>不足为四，<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">五伯</span>不足为六。王若凭人众之广、兵甲之强，乘毁<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">魏</span>之威，而想以武力使<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">天下</span>之主都做<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">臣</span>子，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">臣</span>恐其有后患。《诗》说\"凡事都有开始，却少有<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">克</span>终\"。《易》说\"狐渡水，沾湿尾巴\"。这是说开始容易，终了难。何以知其然？从前<span class=\"dynasty\" title=\"氏族\">智氏</span>见<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">伐</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span>之利而不知<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">榆次</span>之祸，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">吴</span>见<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">伐</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>之便而不知<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">干隧</span>之<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">败</span>。此二国，并非无大功，而是沉溺于眼前之利而忽略了后来的祸患。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">吴</span>信任<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">越</span>，顺从它去<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">伐</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>，既<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">胜</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>人于<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">艾陵</span>，还师却被<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">越</span>王<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">禽</span>于<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">三渚之浦</span>。<span class=\"dynasty\" title=\"氏族\">智氏</span>信任<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">韩</span>、<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">魏</span>，跟从它们去<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">伐</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span>，<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">晋</span><span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">阳城</span>，眼看要胜了，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">韩</span>、<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">魏</span>叛它，在<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">凿台</span>之下<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">杀</span>了<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">智伯瑶</span>。<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">今王</span>嫉恨<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>未毁灭，却忘了毁灭<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>反而使<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">韩</span>、<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">魏</span>强大，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">臣</span>替王考虑而不<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">取</span>这计策。"
    },
    "5": {
      "title": "楚为秦援",
      "text": "《诗》说\"<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">大武</span>远距居住而不涉足\"。从此观之，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>国是盟友，邻国是敌人。《诗》云\"趯趯"
    },
    "6": {
      "title": "韩魏不可信",
      "text": "兔子，还被犬捕获。别人的心思，我可揣度\"。<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">今王</span>中途信任<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">韩</span>、<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">魏</span>友善王，这正和<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">吴</span>信任<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">越</span>一样。<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">臣</span>听说，敌人不可宽容，时机不可错失。<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">臣</span>恐怕<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">韩</span>、<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">魏</span>卑辞除患其实想欺骗大国。为什么？王对<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">韩</span>、<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">魏</span>没有重世之德，却有累世之怨。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">韩</span>、<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">魏</span><span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">父</span>子<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">兄</span>弟接连死于<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>已将<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">十世（时长）</span>了。本国残破，<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">社稷</span>毁坏，<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">宗庙</span>被毁。破腹断肠，折颈断颚，首身分离，尸骨暴露于草泽，头颅僵仆，相望于边境，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">父</span>子老弱系颈束手为<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">群虏</span>者相连于路。<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">鬼神</span>孤独哀伤，无人<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">血食</span>。<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">人民</span>无以为生，<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">族</span>类离散，流亡为<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">仆妾</span>的，遍布海内。所以<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">韩</span>、<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">魏</span>不灭亡，是<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span><span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">社稷</span>的忧患，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">今王</span>借助它们去<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>，岂不太过分吗！"
    },
    "7": {
      "title": "攻楚无利",
      "text": "况且王<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>从哪里出兵？王将借道于仇雠之<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">韩</span>、<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">魏</span>吗？兵出发之日就要忧其不归，这是王把兵借给了仇雠之<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">韩</span>、<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">魏</span>。王若不借道于仇雠之<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">韩</span>、<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">魏</span>，必<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻</span><span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">随水</span>右壤之地。<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">随水</span>右壤，都是<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">广川</span>大水、山林溪谷、不能生产粮食的地方，王即使得到，也不算得地。这是王有毁<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>之名而无得地之实。"
    },
    "8": {
      "title": "四国起兵",
      "text": "况且王<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>之日，四国必都起兵响应王。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>、<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>之兵相持不解，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">魏</span>氏将出兵<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻</span><span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">留</span>、<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">方与</span>、<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">铚</span>、<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">湖陵</span>、<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">砀</span>、<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">萧</span>、<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">相</span>，故<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">宋</span>之地必尽被夺。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>人南面<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>，<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">泗上</span>必被攻取。这些都是<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">平原</span>四通膏腴之地，任它们独<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻</span>。王<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">破</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>反而使<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">韩</span>、<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">魏</span>在<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">中国</span>强大而使<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>劲强。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">韩</span>、<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">魏</span>之强，足以与<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>抗衡。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>南以<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">泗水</span>为境，东背<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">海</span>，北靠<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">黄河</span>，而无后患，<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">天下</span>之国没有比<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>、<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">魏</span>更强的，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>、<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">魏</span>得地葆利且假装事奉下级官吏，<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">一年（时长）</span>之后，虽不能称帝，但足以禁王称帝。"
    },
    "9": {
      "title": "善楚之策",
      "text": "以王土地之广，人众之多，兵甲之强，一举树怨于<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>，反使<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">韩</span>、<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">魏</span>把帝号归给<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>，是王的失计。<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">臣</span>替王考虑，不如善<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>、<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>合而为一以临<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">韩</span>，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">韩</span>必敛手屈服。王倚仗<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">东山</span>之险，拥<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">曲河</span>之利，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">韩</span>必成为<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">关内</span>之<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">侯</span>。若此王以<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">十万</span>戍<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">郑</span>，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">梁</span>氏寒心，<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">许</span>、<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">鄢</span>陵固守，而上<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">蔡</span>、<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">召陵</span>无法往来，如此<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">魏</span>也成为<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">关内</span>之<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">侯</span>了。王一旦善<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>，<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">关内</span><span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">两万乘</span>之主把土地归于<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>右面的地方可拱手而<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">取</span>。王的土地横跨<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">两海</span>，约束<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">天下</span>，这时<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">燕</span>、<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span>无<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>、<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>、<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>无<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">燕</span>、<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span>。然后震动<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">燕</span>、<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span>，直接摇撼<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>、<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>，这四国不等王施压就会归服。"
    },
    "10": {
      "title": "昭王从之",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：秦昭王\">昭王（秦昭王）</span>说：\"好。\" 于是<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">止</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">白起</span>的行动，谢绝<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">韩</span>、<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">魏</span>。派<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">使</span>送礼于<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>，约为盟国。"
    },
    "11": {
      "title": "太子归楚",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">黄歇</span>受命回<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>派<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：黄歇\">歇（黄歇）</span>与<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">太子</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：楚考烈王\">完（楚考烈王）</span>入质于<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>扣留了<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">数年（时长）</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">楚顷襄王</span>病，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">太子</span>不得归。而<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span><span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">太子</span>与<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>相<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">应侯</span>要好，于是<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">黄歇</span>劝<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">应侯</span>说：\"<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">相国</span>真诚对<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span><span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">太子</span>好吗？\" <span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">应侯</span>说：\"是的。\" <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：黄歇\">歇（黄歇）</span>说：\"如今<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>王恐不起病，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>不如放其<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">太子</span>回国。<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">太子</span>得立，他事<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>必重而感激<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">相国</span>无穷，这是亲盟国而得立<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">万乘</span>之主。若不放归，则在<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">咸阳</span>不过一个<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">布衣</span>而已；<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>另外<span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">立</span><span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">太子</span>，必不事<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>。失去盟国又断绝<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">万乘</span>之和，不是上策。愿<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">相国</span>仔细考虑。\" <span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">应侯</span>把此话上报<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>王。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>王说：\"令<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span><span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">太子</span>的<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">傅</span>先去探问<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>王之病，回来之后再图之。\" <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">黄歇</span>为<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span><span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">太子</span>计议说：\"<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>扣留<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">太子</span>，是想求利。如今<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">太子</span>无力利于<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：黄歇\">歇（黄歇）</span>十分忧虑。而阳<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">文君</span>的<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">子</span><span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">二人</span>在国中，王若一旦故去，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">太子</span>不在，阳<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">文君</span>之<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">子</span>必立为后嗣，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">太子</span>就不能奉<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">宗庙</span>了。不如逃离<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>，与<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">使者</span>一同出关；<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">臣</span>请求留下，以死担当此事。\" <span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span><span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">太子</span>因而改换<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">衣服</span>为<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span><span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">使者</span>的御者出关，而<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">黄歇</span>守住居所，常说有病谢客。估计<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">太子</span>已远行，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>追不及，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：黄歇\">歇（黄歇）</span>便主动向<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">秦昭王</span>说：\"<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span><span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">太子</span>已归，走远了。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：黄歇\">歇（黄歇）</span><span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">当死</span>，请赐我一死。\" <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：秦昭王\">昭王（秦昭王）</span>大怒，想准其<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">自杀</span>。<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">应侯</span>说：\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：黄歇\">歇（黄歇）</span>作为<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">人臣</span>，舍身为其主，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">太子</span>立位，必用<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：黄歇\">歇（黄歇）</span>，所以不如无罪放回，以亲善<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>。\" <span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>便放<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">黄歇</span>回国。"
    },
    "12": {
      "title": "春申君为相",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：黄歇\">歇（黄歇）</span>到<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span><span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">三月（时长）</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">楚顷襄王</span>去世，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">太子</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：楚考烈王\">完（楚考烈王）</span>即位，就是<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">考烈王</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">考烈王</span><span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">元年</span>，任<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">黄歇</span>为<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">相</span>，<span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">封</span>他为<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">春申君</span>，赐<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">淮北</span>之地<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">十二县</span>。<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">十五年（时长）</span>后，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">黄歇</span>对<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>王说：\"<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">淮北</span>之地靠<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>，那里事务紧急，请立为郡更便利。\" 便一并献出<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">淮北</span><span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">十二县</span>。请封于<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">江东</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">考烈王</span>答应了。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">春申君</span>便在旧<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">吴</span>墟建城，以此自建都邑。"
    },
    "13": {
      "title": "四君争下士",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">春申君</span>既相<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>，当时<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>有<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">孟尝君</span>，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span>有<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">平原君</span>，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">魏</span>有<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">信陵君</span>，都在<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">争</span>相招纳<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">士</span>人，招致<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">宾客</span>，以此相互倾夺，辅佐<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">国</span>政、掌握权柄。"
    },
    "14": {
      "title": "救赵伐鲁",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">春申君</span>做<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>相<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">四年（时长）</span>，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">破</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span>在<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">长平</span>之军<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">四十馀万</span>。<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">五年（时长）</span>，<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">围</span><span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">邯郸</span>。<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">邯郸</span>向<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>告急，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>派<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">春申君</span>领兵前去<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">救</span>援，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>兵也撤离，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">春申君</span>返回。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">春申君</span>相<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span><span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">八年（时长）</span>，为<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>北<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">伐</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">灭</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">鲁</span>，任<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">荀卿</span>为<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">兰陵</span>令。当时，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>又强盛。"
    },
    "15": {
      "title": "珠履炫客",
      "text": "赵<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">平原君</span>派人到<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">春申君</span>处，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">春申君</span>把他们安置在上舍。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span><span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">使</span>想向<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>炫耀，用<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">玳瑁</span>做<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">簪</span>，刀<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">剑</span>鞘以珠<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">玉</span>装饰，请求见<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">春申君</span><span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">客</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">春申君</span><span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">客</span><span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">三千馀人</span>，其<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">上客</span>都穿<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">珠履</span>见<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span><span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">使</span>，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span><span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">使</span>大惭。"
    },
    "16": {
      "title": "吕不韦相秦",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">春申君</span>相<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">十四年（时长）</span>，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">庄襄王</span>即位，任<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">吕不韦</span>为<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">相</span>，封为<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">文信侯</span>。夺取东<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">周</span>。"
    },
    "17": {
      "title": "合纵败函谷",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">春申君</span>相<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">二十二年（时长）</span>，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">诸侯</span>忧虑<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>不断<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">伐</span>，于是相与<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">合从</span>，西<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">伐</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>王为<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">从长</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">春申君</span>掌事。到<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">函谷关</span>，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>出兵<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻</span>，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">诸侯</span>兵都<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">败</span>走。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">考烈王</span>为此归咎于<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">春申君</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">春申君</span>从此被疏远。"
    },
    "18": {
      "title": "朱英之言",
      "text": "有客人<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">观津</span>人<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">硃英</span>，对<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">春申君</span>说：\"人们都以为<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>强而<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">君</span>用之而弱，在我看来不然。先<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">君</span>时善待<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span><span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">二十年（时长）</span>而<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>不<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>，为什么？<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>逾黾隘之塞而<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>，不便；借道于两<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">周</span>，背<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">韩</span>、<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">魏</span>去<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>，不可。如今不同，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">魏</span>旦夕将亡，不能爱惜<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">许</span>、<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">鄢</span>陵，它许诺把<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">魏</span>地割给<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>兵离<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">陈</span>只有<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">百六十里</span>，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">臣</span>所看到的，是<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>、<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>将天天交战。\" <span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>便离开<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">陈</span>迁至<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">寿春</span>；而<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>迁<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">卫</span>于<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">野王</span>，设置<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">东郡</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">春申君</span>从此去了自己封邑<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">吴</span>，以封地处理相事。"
    },
    "19": {
      "title": "献女进楚",
      "text": "<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">考烈王</span>无<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">子</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">春申君</span>为此忧虑，寻求宜生<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">子</span>的<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">妇人</span>献上，很多，终无<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">子</span>。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span>人<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">李园</span>带着他的<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">女</span><span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">弟</span>（妹妹），想献给<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>王，听说<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>王不宜生子，怕久而不得宠。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">李园</span>请求事奉<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">春申君</span>为<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">舍人</span>，后来请假回家，故意逾期。回来谒见，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">春申君</span>问他原因，他回答说：\"<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>王派<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">使</span>者来求<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">臣</span>的<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">女</span><span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">弟</span>，与其<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">使</span>者饮酒，所以逾期。\" <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">春申君</span>说：\"聘定了吗？\" 回答说：\"还没有。\" <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">春申君</span>说：\"可以见吗？\" <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">李园</span>说：\"可以。\" 于是<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">李园</span>便把他的<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">女</span><span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">弟</span>献进，立即被<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">春申君</span>宠幸。知道她有了身孕，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">李园</span>便与他的<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">女</span><span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">弟</span>密谋。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：李园\">园（李园）</span><span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">女</span><span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">弟</span>找机会对<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">春申君</span>说：\"<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>王宠幸<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">君</span>，虽<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">兄</span>弟也不如。如今<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">君</span>相<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span><span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">二十多年（时长）</span>，王无<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">子</span>，一旦<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">百年（时长）</span>之后，将改立<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">兄</span>弟之子，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>国另立<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">君</span>之后嗣，也必各亲近自己的故旧，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">君</span>又怎能长保宠信呢？并非只是这样，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">君</span>掌权已久，多次失礼于王<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">兄</span>弟，他们一旦立为王，祸患将及身，怎能保住<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">相</span><span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">印</span>和<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">江东</span>之封？如今妾自知有身孕了，而人不知。妾被<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">君</span>宠幸不久，若以<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">君</span>之重将妾献给<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>王，王必宠幸<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">妾</span>；妾若赖天得<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">子</span>男，那就是<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">君</span>之<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">子</span>为王，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>国尽归所得，比起身临不测之罪怎么样？\" <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">春申君</span>深以为然，便把<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">李园</span><span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">女</span><span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">弟</span>送出，慎重安置并对<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>王说。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>王召入宠幸她，便生下<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">子</span>男，<span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">立</span>为<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">太子</span>，以<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">李园</span><span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">女</span><span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">弟</span>为王后。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>王贵<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">李园</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：李园\">园（李园）</span>掌权。"
    },
    "20": {
      "title": "李园阴养死士",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">李园</span>既已把<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">女</span><span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">弟</span>献进宫，<span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">立</span>为<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">王后</span>，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">子</span>为<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">太子</span>，担心<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">春申君</span>泄露而益发骄纵，暗中养<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">死士</span>，想<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">杀</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">春申君</span>以<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">灭口</span>，而<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">国人</span>颇有知道的。"
    },
    "21": {
      "title": "朱英三问",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">春申君</span>相<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">二十五年（时长）</span>，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">考烈王</span>病。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">硃英</span>对<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">春申君</span>说：\"世上有毋望之福，又有毋望之祸。如今<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">君</span>处毋望之世，事毋望之主，怎能没有毋望之人呢？\" <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">春申君</span>说：\"什么叫毋望之福？\" <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">硃英</span>说：\"<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">君</span>相<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span><span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">二十多年（时长）</span>了，虽名<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">相国</span>，实为<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>王。如今<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>王病，旦夕将卒，而<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">君</span>辅佐<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">少主</span>，由此代立主政，如<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">伊尹</span>、<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">周公</span>那样，王长大之后归<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">政</span>于王，或南面称孤独占<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>国？这就是所谓毋望之福。\" <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">春申君</span>说：\"什么叫毋望之祸？\" <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">硃英</span>说：\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">李园</span>不治国却是<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">君</span>之仇，他不为兵事而养<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">死士</span>已<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">日久（时长）</span>，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>王一卒，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">李园</span>必抢先入宫据权<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">杀</span><span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">君</span>以<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">灭口</span>。这就是所谓毋望之祸。\" <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">春申君</span>说：\"什么叫毋望之人？\" <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">硃英</span>回答说：\"<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">君</span>任<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">臣</span>为<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">郎中</span>，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>王一卒，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">李园</span>必抢先入宫，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">臣</span>替<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">君</span><span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">杀</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">李园</span>。这就是所谓毋望之人。\" <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">春申君</span>说：\"足下算了吧，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">李园</span>是懦弱之人，我又善待他，况且又怎会到这种地步！\" <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">硃英</span>知道他不采纳自己的建议，怕祸及身，便逃走。"
    },
    "22": {
      "title": "春申君被杀",
      "text": "后<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">十七天（时长）</span>，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">考烈王</span>卒，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">李园</span>果然先入，把<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">死士</span>埋伏在<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">棘门</span>之内。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">春申君</span>入<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">棘门</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：李园\">园（李园）</span><span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">死士</span>从两边<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">刺</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">春申君</span>，<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">斩</span>其头，投出<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">棘门</span>外。于是派<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">吏</span>尽<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">灭</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">春申君</span>之<span class=\"dynasty\" title=\"氏族\">家</span>。而<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">李园</span><span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">女</span><span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">弟</span>初幸<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">春申君</span>时所怀后入王宫所生之<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">子</span>便立为王，就是<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：楚幽王\">幽王（楚幽王）</span>。"
    },
    "23": {
      "title": "始皇九年",
      "text": "这年，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">秦始皇</span>帝即位<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">九年（时长）</span>了。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">嫪毐</span>也在<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>作乱，被发觉，<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">夷</span>其<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">三族</span>，而<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">吕不韦</span>被废。"
    },
    "24": {
      "title": "太史公曰",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">太史公</span>说：我到过<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>，看过<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">春申君</span>的旧城，<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">宫室</span>十分盛美！当初，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">春申君</span>游说<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">秦昭王</span>，及舍身送<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span><span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">太子</span>归国，是多么聪明啊！后来被<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">李园</span>制住，年老糊涂了。俗话说：\"当断不断，反受其乱。\" <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">春申君</span>不用<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">硃英</span>，说的就是这种情况吧？"
    },
    "25": {
      "title": "赞",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">黄歇</span>辩智，权略<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>、<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>。 <span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">太子</span>获归，身作宰辅。 珠炫<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span>客，邑开<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">吴</span>土。 <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：楚考烈王\">烈王（楚考烈王）</span>少嗣，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">李园</span>献<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">女</span>。 无妄之灾成祸，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">硃英</span>徒然进谏。"
    }
  }
}